Added Progress Bar to Loading webviews. Added structure for Refresh button in action bar.

Revised main activity. Fixed fragment handling. Added icons to experiment with in drawer menu. Removed About Fragment. Fixed crashing issue and path build error.

Added map pins using data from sqlite3 db. Refactored connection check to class
